Doctor Who - Big Finish Podcast 06 - 03-17-2008

(17/03/2008)
In this weeks Big Finish Podcast we have Eddie Robson&#039;s top five stories; Eddie is the producer of our Bernice Summerfield series. This week also sees the release of some of our Companion Chronicles for download, so in honour of that we give you tasters of Old Soldiers and Mother Russia. Also, like every week, we have all the latest news from Big Finish in a nice easy poddable chunk.

Eddie Robson&#039;s Top Five:
Omega
Sympathy for the Devil
The Chimes of Midnight
The Final Amendment
Immortal Beloved
